<p><strong>Medium plant, lawful neutral</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 18 (natural armor, shield)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 75 (10d8+30)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft., climb 30 ft.</p>

